liboop
------------------------------------------
Liboop is a low-level event loop management library for POSIX-based operating
systems. It supports the development of modular, multiplexed applications
which may respond to events from several sources. It replaces the select()
loop and allows the registration of event handlers for file and network I/O,
timers and signals. Since processes use these mechanisms for almost all
external communication, liboop can be used as the basis for almost any
application.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.9.0-3
  cygwin-devel-2.9.0-3
  libglib2.0-devel-2.52.3-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.52.3-1
  liboop-devel-1.0.1-1bl1
  liboop-glib2-devel-1.0.1-1bl1
  liboop-glib2_0-1.0.1-1bl1
  liboop-rl0-1.0.1-1bl1
  liboop-tcl0-1.0.1-1bl1
  liboop4-1.0.1-1bl1
  libreadline7-7.0.3-3
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1
  tcl-8.6.6-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-10-1
  binutils-2.28-3
  cygport-0.24.1-1
  gcc-core-6.4.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-5
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  http://www.lysator.liu.se/liboop/

Canonical download:
  http://ftp.lysator.liu.se/pub/liboop/liboop-1.0.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack liboop-1.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./liboop-1.0.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/liboop-1.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop4-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-devel-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-glib2_0-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-glib2-devel-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-rl0-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-rl-devel-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-tcl0-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-tcl-devel-1.0.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(liboop)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/liboop.README
  /usr/share/doc/liboop/COPYING

(liboop4)
  /usr/bin/cygoop-4.dll

(liboop-devel)
  /usr/include/oop-read.h
  /usr/include/oop.h
  /usr/lib/liboop.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/liboop.pc

(liboop-glib2_0)
  /usr/bin/cygoop-glib2-0.dll

(liboop-glib2-devel)
  /usr/include/oop-glib.h
  /usr/lib/liboop-glib2.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/liboop-glib2.pc

(liboop-rl0)
  /usr/bin/cygoop-rl-0.dll

(liboop-rl-devel)
  /usr/include/oop-rl.h
  /usr/lib/liboop-rl.dll.a

(liboop-tcl0)
  /usr/bin/cygoop-tcl-0.dll

(liboop-tcl-devel)
  /usr/include/oop-tcl.h
  /usr/lib/liboop-tcl.dll.a

